            <title><![CDATA[【倒头就睡可能是一种病[费解][费解][费解]】说起良好睡眠，很多人想到的可能都是不失眠，说睡就睡。事实上，睡得太快、睡得太多也不一定好，那可能是得了一种名...]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[【倒头就睡可能是一种病<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[费解]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_feijie-c1df37ef03.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="url-icon"><img alt="[费解]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_feijie-c1df37ef03.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="url-icon"><img alt="[费解]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_feijie-c1df37ef03.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>】说起良好睡眠，很多人想到的可能都是不失眠，说睡就睡。事实上，睡得太快、睡得太多也不一定好，那可能是得了一种名叫“发作性睡病”的罕见病。那么，究竟什么是“发作性睡病”？真正的良好睡眠又有什么标准呢？👇🏻（出品：科普中国-<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%88%9B%E4%BD%9C%E5%9F%B9%E8%82%B2%E8%AE%A1%E5%88%92%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%88%9B%E4%BD%9C%E5%9F%B9%E8%82%B2%E8%AE%A1%E5%88%92%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#创作培育计划#</span></a> ） <a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034:4917626946912343" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_video_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="surl-text">科普中国的微博视频</span></a><br clear="both"><div style="clear: both"></div><video controls="controls" poster="https://tvax2.sinaimg.cn/orj480/005ztyuLly1hfe1nnxxgfj61hc0u0tqb02.jpg" style="width: 100%"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/R9t9gMOZlx086AD19URi01041201Jzms0E010.mp4?label=mp4_720p&amp;template=1280x720.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1688030275&amp;ssig=XW7bygnze2&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/W26gU4gwlx086AD1MUbe01041200SOBh0E010.mp4?label=mp4_hd&amp;template=852x480.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1688030275&amp;ssig=Q%2FnBnEuHJU&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/UOZ3Xlh0lx086AD0sNVm01041200yzFl0E010.mp4?label